 carried out. Our results are broadly\nconsistent with a galactic fountain origin combined with gas accretion.\nHowever, a dynamical model is required to better understand the formation of\nionised extraplanar gas.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 12 Apr 2021 18:03:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-21"}
