rage vehicle delay and intersection\ncapacity. Further, the SPDL-based model is extended to serve as an alternative\napproach without the buffer zone.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 06:00:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-14"}
