oller is\nable to stabilize dynamic and algebraic states under significant disturbances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 06:10:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Feb 2023 15:50:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-09"}
