ity provides an additional knob to control the cascade of the\ndelocalization transition besides the on-site potential.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 13 Apr 2021 09:05:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 24 Apr 2021 12:47:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-07"}
